title: Mastery Pages not loading properly
body: A couple of times my mastery pages haven't loaded ingame. it seems to not work if you change in the last 1 sec before the game starts

replies.body:
I blamed myself for not making sure I clicked the right page but I've possibly had this issue a few times as well.

edit: wait do you mean the wrong page loaded or you had no masteries at all. I may have misunderstood.
Yeah i had no masteries at all.
